name: VNCoreMLFeatureValueObservation
desc: An object that represents a collection of key-value information that a Core ML image analysis request produces.

items.name: var featureValue: MLFeatureValue
items.desc: The feature result of a VNCoreMLRequest that outputs neither a classification nor an image.

items.name: var featureName: String
items.desc: The name used in the model description of the CoreML model that produced this observation.
